By":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"對敵人有良知係對自己殘忍<br />\n醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be7f8eac6a8c500cafc647d44eab1f512d626ea","tid":1958274,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"其實所有人勇武反抗會贏<br />\n所有人瘋狂登記功能組別會贏<br />\n所有人只幫襯黄色經濟圈未必會贏，但會嚇到對家商鋪<br />\n<br />\n要做到呢d就係要齊心<br />\n人多左就會唔同意見，所以先要強調唔批鬥，核彈都唔割<br />\n有d野你覺得十惡不赦，但我覺得無乜所謂，你就算嘈交嘈贏我都冇用㗎，咁不如嘈少陣做其他野"},{"pid":"a6e9b8b1a4bea4a25039baa9ec2e5324bcc74bd6","tid":1958274,"uid":203685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05438ec31b88ec7cd59751fa7d3003fba9d828b3","tid":1958274,"uid":280329,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:35:43.000Z","msg":"班藍絲廢老值得我地學習既係 <br />\n佢地真係冇左膠會阻撚住自己人做野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>-0-0</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"到左今日 左膠已經唔算係自己人了<br />\n<br />\n-0-0"},{"pid":"3a88f07d5d7ce326585c9e4c2cbc29dcf26d63c8","tid":1958274,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀 見有個po連689條死廢老都大把人留言認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e4a47b305b3390c9469de288d23e52397c296c","tid":1958274,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a88f07d5d7ce326585c9e4c2cbc29dcf26d63c8","tid":1958274,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"啱呀 見有個po連689條死廢老都大把人留言認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a525cf9d56d604d3eb07a8dab02edef63b8a5deb","tid":1958274,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc76478f3534bbe867b7e0fe1e5be4c8f04b136e","tid":1958274,"uid":147895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"970069a801a72cb735bb671a9c0a825d339d3872","tid":1958274,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"但係自己陣營 過份自我批判<br />\n就會變咗內鬥<br />\n所以藍屍嗰套都值得借鏡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"我篇野就係講梗你前兩句同後兩句無關係<br />\n因為兩邊本質差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"藍屍: 只要方向目標正確<br />\n道德擺撚埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n黃絲: 所謂黃藍是良知<br />\n佢出嚟抗爭<br />\n並非因為&quot;自己係香港人&quot;<br />\n&quot;有責任 有義務 守護香港&quot;<br />\n而係因為佢出於&quot;良知&quot;<br />\n所以先做黃絲<br />\n<br />\n故此 黃絲係比較多嘢諗<br />\n尤其諗好多道德尺嚟批判自己人<br />\n內鬥其中一個因素就係咁<br />\n<br />\n你睇返龍門冰室<br />\n被人鬥到貼街招<br />\n絕大部分<br />\n(包括話佢寫app搶c4v生意)<br />\n都係鬥緊一間公司嘅企業道德<br />\n實際上龍門<br />\n未有交過任何手足個人資料畀警甴<br />\n(暫未有証據)<br />\n<br />\n咁有咩好鬥？<br />\n因為啲人企喺道德高地<br />\n黃絲個個<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[url](當自己)[/url]</span>聖人嚟<br />\n<br />\n本土撚/手足<br />\n根本就唔柒在乎呢啲"},{"pid":"d5ce82dd5777e0afa8ee986d37dfa35a4fe8b6b2","tid":1958274,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2c238172b824f3cb1ccc5cb28cbe4a84fae6ad","tid":1958274,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"有良心地輸 其實都係件好事 <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界無得比你又得魚又得熊掌<br />\n<br />\n又想要良心又想贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"輸 就要檢討<br />\n唔撚係安慰自己 &quot;有良心地輸&quot;<br />\n<br />\n歷史係勝利者所寫<br />\n唔係邊個有良心 邊個寫<br />\n我真係唔想自己啲孫(如果有嘅話)<br />\n會話阿爺當年係暴徒 反政府<br />\n警甴就止暴制亂 抗暴英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefed0bf6bc17013683a7ee73ab6b433efac1d6b","tid":1958274,"uid":295442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"